/wiki/Aleksandar_Cvetkovi\u0107: Aleksandar Cvetković (Serbian Cyrillic: Александар Цветковић, born September 12, 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player for Baxi Manresa of the Spanish Liga ACB.
/wiki/KK_Crvena_zvezda: Košarkaški klub Crvena zvezda (Serbian Cyrillic: Кошаркашки клуб Црвена звезда, English: Red Star Basketball Club), commonly referred to as KK Crvena zvezda mts for sponsorship reasons or simply Crvena zvezda, is a men's professional basketball club based in Belgrade, Serbia, the major part of the Red Star multi-sports club. The club is a founding member and shareholder of the Adriatic Basketball Association,  and competes in the ABA League, the EuroLeague and in the Basketball League of Serbia.
/wiki/Nikola_Radi\u010devi\u0107: Nikola Radičević (Serbian: Никола Радичевић, born April 25, 1994) is a Serbian professional basketball player for UCAM Murcia of the Liga ACB. Standing at 6 ft 5 in (1.96 m), he plays at the point guard position.
/wiki/KK_Partizan: Košarkaški klub Partizan (Serbian Cyrillic: Кошаркашки клуб Партизан, English: Partizan Basketball Club), commonly referred to as KK Partizan or simply Partizan, is a men's professional basketball club based in Belgrade, Serbia. It is part of the multi-sports Belgrade-based club Partizan. The club is a founding member and shareholder of the Adriatic Basketball Association, and competes in the ABA League, the EuroCup and in the Basketball League of Serbia.
/wiki/Marko_Radonji\u0107: Marko Radonjić (Serbian Cyrillic: Марко Радоњић, born February 6, 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player for Balkan Botevgrad of the Bulgarian League.
/wiki/Nemanja_Dangubi\u0107: Nemanja Dangubić (Serbian: Немања Дангубић, born April 13, 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player for Movistar Estudiantes of the Liga ACB. He was selected by the Philadelphia 76ers with the 54th overall pick in the 2014 NBA draft.
/wiki/Nikola_\u010cvorovi\u0107: Nikola Čvorović (Serbian Cyrillic: Никола Чворовић, born 30 January 1994) is a Serbian professional basketball player for Kolubara LA 2003 of the Basketball League of Serbia.
/wiki/Luka_Mitrovi\u0107: Luka Mitrović (Serbian: Лука Митровић, born 21 March 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player who last played for UCAM Murcia of the Liga ACB. Standing at 6 ft 9 in (2.06 m), he plays at the power forward position. Mitrovic was the final selection of the 2015 NBA draft.
/wiki/KK_Hemofarm: Košarkaški klub Vršac (Serbian Cyrillic: Кошаркашки клуб Вршац), commonly referred to as KK Vršac, is a men's professional basketball club based in Vršac, Serbia. They are currently competing in the Basketball League of Serbia. Their home arena is the Millennium Centar, with a capacity of 4,400.
/wiki/Nenad_Miljenovi\u0107: Nenad Miljenović (Serbian Cyrillic: Ненад Миљеновић; born April 8, 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player for OKK Beograd of the Basketball League of Serbia. Standing at 1.94 m (6 ft 4 1⁄2 in), he plays at the point guard position.
/wiki/KK_FMP_(1991\u20132011): Košarkaški klub FMP (Serbian Cyrillic: Кошаркашки клуб ФMП), commonly referred to as KK FMP, was a men's professional basketball club based in Belgrade, Serbia. The club played its home games at the 3,000 capacity Železnik Hall and have won the regional ABA League twice, in the 2003–04 and 2005–06 seasons.
/wiki/Nemanja_Krsti\u0107: Nemanja Krstić (Serbian Cyrillic: Немања Крстић, born March 2, 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player for Szolnoki Olaj of the Hungarian Nemzeti Bajnokság I/A (NB I/A). He also representde the Serbian national basketball team in the international competitions. Standing at 6 ft 8 in (2.03 m), he can play either shooting guard and small forward positions.
/wiki/Nikola_Jankovi\u0107_(basketball): Nikola Janković (Serbian: Никола Јанковић, born February 13, 1994) is a Serbian professional basketball player for Partizan of the Basketball League of Serbia. Standing at 2.06 m (6 ft 9 in), he plays the power forward position.
/wiki/\u0110or\u0111e_Milo\u0161evi\u010: Đorđe Milošević (Serbian Cyrillic: Ђорђе Милошевић, born 20 June 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player who plays for MZT Skopje in ABA League Second Division and Macedonian First League.
/wiki/Nemanja_Bezbradica: Nemanja Bezbradica (Serbian: Немања Безбрадица, born 29 March 1993) is a Serbian professional basketball player.
